data.description: Charming 1929 Cape Cod nestled on a corner lot beautifully landscaped overlooking the Pawcatuck River...Oh the sunsets you'll see! This ideal location offers original hardwoods on the main level with a new kitchen just completed in 2023, and two first floor bedrooms that could easily opt as home office or playroom. A cozy spacious living room with a wood burning fireplace flows into a formal dining room with coffered ceilings in both rooms and plenty of windows which add such a special touch to the home. Upstairs you will discover plentiful sun filled space including the master bedroom with a sitting room that can be used as a dressing room, nursery, home office or lounging area.  A generous full bath has a jacuzzi tub, shower stall and a footprint that could easily be redesigned to suit your personal needs.  Further down the hallway is a 14’x15’ fourth bedroom large enough for a few beds overlooking the Pawcatuck River.  Closet space and eave storage this charmer does not lack.  Central air throughout with 5 forced air splits.  LOCATION is key with walkability to the river and the Westerly Yacht Club. Short ride to our area’s beautiful beaches, yet convenient to downtown, restaurants, theatres and shopping. The list of updates are available.
